{
  "title": "Luxurious Silky Croatian Tempeh Stir fry",
  "description": "A high-protein Croatian dish featuring tempeh, perfect for a date night, with a jammy and silky texture, this stir-fry is a must try for any food lover.",
  "cuisine": "Croatian",
